cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

This paper is about a robotic auto-focus system that uses deep reinforcement learning. The focus is on the application of the method to robotics, which suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) category. However, the method also involves visual input and learning control policies, which are related to Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) categories. Additionally, the use of reinforcement learning suggests that the paper could also belong to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) category.
